td.p:
This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of Article 311(1)(1) of Council Directive 2006/112/EC of 28 November 2006 on the common system of value added tax (
OJ 2006 L 347, p. 1
).

Recital 5 of Directive 2000/53/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 18 September 2000 on end-of life vehicles (
OJ 2000 L 269, p. 34
) provides that there is a fundamental principle that waste should be reused and recovered, and that preference be given to reuse and recycling. Recital 14 of that directive acknowledges the need to encourage the development of markets for recycled materials.
